pyasf - symbolic computing of anisotropic resonant scattering factor 
*************************************************************

Author:  Carsten Richter
Contact: carsten.richter@desy.de
      or carsten.richter@physik.tu-freiberg.de
Website: http://desy.de/~crichter/



Requirements:
    - python 2
    - Python Packages:
        - numpy
        - sympy
	- PyCifRW
    - the package rexs (https://github.com/carichte/rexs)
        is recommended and necessary for DAFS evaluation


